# LFS is intentionally unused. After PRQ-01 + gltf-transform optimize the entire
# converted asset tree (5 character GLBs + 10 prop GLBs + 50 trap GLBs + HDRI +
# textures) totals ~60 MB — well within reasonable raw-blob territory for a
# single repo. The cd.yml LFS-after-build pattern from grovekeeper / chonkers
# is therefore not needed here. Re-enable LFS only if total weight exceeds
# ~250 MB or git operations get slow.

# Normalize line endings on text
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.bat text eol=crlf

# Treat lockfiles as generated — collapse in PR diffs
pnpm-lock.yaml linguist-generated
